  "tutorial": {
    "title": "Tutorial",
    "subtitle": "Learn how to use ConciergeDesk",
    "intro": "ConciergeDesk is a complete management platform for luxury concierge services. It helps you manage clients, service providers, requests, communications, and analytics — all in one place. Here's a guide to each section.",
    "dashboard_title": "Dashboard",
    "dashboard_content": "Your home screen shows an overview of activity: total clients, providers, active requests, and margins. You'll also see recent requests, upcoming client arrivals, and an AI-powered daily briefing that summarizes what needs your attention today.",
    "clients_title": "Clients",
    "clients_content": "Add and manage your clients with details like name, email, phone, hotel, arrival/departure dates, and personal preferences (diet, allergies, budget tier, preferred services). You can import clients in bulk via CSV. Click any client to see their full profile and request history.",
    "providers_title": "Providers",
    "providers_content": "Manage your service providers (chefs, tour guides, yacht companies, etc.). Each provider has a category, reliability score, commission percentage, and contact info. Click a provider to see their availability calendar, request history, and performance metrics.",
    "requests_title": "Requests",
    "requests_content": "Create and track service requests for your clients. Each request has a service type, date, budget, description, and status. The status follows a workflow: Draft → Sent → Waiting → Confirmed → Completed (or Cancelled). You can assign providers, compare quotes, and track margins.",
    "messages_title": "Messages",
    "messages_content": "A built-in messaging system to communicate with clients and providers. Create conversations linked to specific requests, use pre-built message templates, or let AI generate professional messages for you. Supports in-app, WhatsApp, and email channels.",
    "analytics_title": "Analytics",
    "analytics_content": "View performance metrics including total revenue, margins, requests per month, service distribution by category, and provider performance rankings. Use this data to optimize your operations and identify top performers.",
    "import_title": "CSV Import",
    "import_content": "Import clients or providers in bulk using CSV files. The import wizard automatically maps columns (supports Italian, English, and Spanish headers), lets you preview data before importing, and handles common formatting issues like BOM characters and mixed delimiters.",
    "ai_title": "AI Features",
    "ai_content": "AI is integrated throughout the app:\n• AI Extract: Paste a free-text request and AI fills in structured fields automatically\n• AI Suggest: Get provider recommendations based on availability, reliability, and cost\n• AI Generate: Create professional messages for clients or providers\n• Daily Briefing: Get an AI summary of today's arrivals, pending tasks, and revenue",
    "availability_title": "Provider Availability",
    "availability_content": "Each provider has an availability calendar. Set available dates, time slots, and capacity. When assigning providers to requests, the system checks availability to help you avoid conflicts and overbooking.",
    "settings_title": "Settings",
    "settings_content": "Update your profile information (name, email) and choose your preferred interface language (Italian, English, or Spanish). All changes are saved to your account.",
    "tips_title": "Pro Tips",
    "tip_1": "Use the AI Daily Briefing every morning to quickly see what needs attention.",
    "tip_2": "Set up provider availability calendars to speed up assignment decisions.",
    "tip_3": "Use message templates for common communications to save time.",
    "tip_4": "Check Analytics regularly to identify your most profitable services and best providers."
  },
